      "content": "it felt way more intense than just a coincidence though. like, it wasn't just seeing the guy, it was like the whole atmosphere reset for a second. almost like the environment was being reused to save on something? i've been thinking lately that maybe we aren't in a physical world at all. do u think its possible we're living in some kind of simulation and i'm just starting to see the seams?",
